	BST_PIXDATA_EMPTY1x1 as menu item image instead of pixdata
	with invalid magic.

	* beast-gtk/bstutils.h: provide a serialized pixdata empty 1x1
	pixel image macro: BST_PIXDATA_EMPTY1x1.

